  "keyFeatures": [
    "JavaScript API for customizing Kintone app UI and responding to user events",
    "REST API for programmatic management of apps, records, files, and spaces",
    "Event system covering record list, detail, create, edit, print, graph, portal, and space pages",
    "Plug-in support for both JS API configuration and REST API management",
    "Desktop and mobile support for all major APIs",
    "Proxy support for external API requests from within Kintone customizations"
